experiment SP_NI_CUSP
instrument ESR
start 2017 12 22 0700
end 2017 12 22 1100
status R
description Observation of the mesoscale structure and dynamics of the plasma flow toward the cusp
contact Satoshi Taguchi
phone +81-75-753-3951
