submitter Y. Ogawa (yogawa@nipr.ac.jp)
resources NI(4)
notes
This investigates the mesoscale structure and dynamics of the plasma flow toward
the cusp, using simultaneous observations between the ESR 32-m radar and an
all-sky imager. 

